main event: A witness reported seeing two unidentified flying objects in Wilmington, Delaware on October 5, 1966.
interesting points: The objects were described as a small white pin-sized dot and a larger glowing red object that moved at a rapid speed., The sighting lasted for a total of 3 to 5 minutes., The red object changed colors from bluish white to greenish white before becoming reddish-orange., The witness has experience working with aircraft and noted these lights were unlike any they had seen before., The objects were reported to be moving in a westward direction.
sighted object: two unidentified flying objects, one bright white light and one glowing red object
witness description: A male, age 22, with experience at airfields and prior exposure to aircraft.
